Commentary Text: Nadeem to de Villiers, out Caught by Abhishek Sharma!! Was on the cards! He was never looking to keep the ball down with those boundary shots. Flatter delivery outside off stump, de Villiers wants to clear the deep cover fence after going back a touch, instead hits it flat and low and down the throat of the fielder there. Oh RCB, can't dent their chances at the business end against SRH again! If you are an RCB fan you have every right to be disappointed with AB for throwing it away. Got set, had to bat through to bail the team out. Boundaries would have taken care of itself. de Villiers c Abhishek Sharma b Nadeem 24(24) [4s-1 6s-1]
